Log Collection > Metric Analysis
Metric Analysis > Alert Trigger

Alert Trigger > Receive Pager : Critical Threshold Exceeded
Alert Trigger --> Log Collection : Normal

Receive Pager > Triage Issue
Triage Issue > Fix Deployed : Quick Fix
Triage Issue > Root Cause Analysis : Complex Issue

Root Cause Analysis > System Update
System Update > Fix Deployed
